main event: A newspaper reporter reported witnessing a flash of light identified as a UFO seen over La Crosse, Wisconsin, which was observed at high speeds.
interesting points: The object was described as a flash of light with many witnesses reporting the sighting., John Henrich, a reporter, claimed to have seen two bright saucer-shaped objects., The incident was reported by local residents in West Salem and La Crosse., Officials received multiple calls reporting the sighting, but no explanation was found., Local airport officials and Civil Aeronautics Administration personnel reported seeing nothing unusual.
sighted object: flash of light flying at high speed
witness description: John Henrich, reporter for the La Crosse Tribune
